title:      Typography
---

<p class="v2-copy">Typography helps create the structure and hierarchy of a page. This helps users read, absorb and comprehend the content. We use Roboto for headings and Open Sans for body and UI elements.</p>

<p class="v2-copy">These typefaces were chosen for their pairing, extensive range of weights and similarity to Helvetica.</p>
<p class="v2-copy"><a href="http://www.fontsquirrel.com/fonts/download/roboto" class="v2-link v2-link--green">Download Roboto for desktop</a><br />
<a href="http://www.fontsquirrel.com/fonts/download/open-sans" class="v2-link v2-link--green">Download Open Sans for desktop</a></p>


